nodes.title: README
widgets_values:
Very important, must read.

- Recommended node for HD restoration, use this zoom node if you want a more realistic image, even including pore detail. https://openart.ai/workflows/seven947/1minute-8k-upscale/1IPTks1gL7v0EPmvsMcx

This node of mine uses Yoloworld to recognize objects, not just just redraw faces and hair, you can combine them as you like.

1. the many / many prople node turns on if there are many people, if there are many people then split the mask and redraw each character individually, otherwise redraw them all together. 2. if the hair is recognized when the hair is recognized then use this zoom node.

2. If you recognize the whole head when you recognize the hair, please adjust the first parameter in Yoloworld ESAM.

3. I use RemapImageRange to pass the image, if you don't want to pass you can disable the node.

How to use high and low frequency: measured high CFG and high noise reduction can greatly increase the details of the screen, but the character face will become black, low frequency is the same reason, if you know PS, you can use the mask to scrape to get a very good picture effect.

nodes.title: Version updates and open source agreements
widgets_values:
Version number v1.0.3
- Known issue: Face gets darker as redraw magnitude and facial details increase.
- Fixed, the third node connection error.
- New node style adding pictures, avoiding the error of subsequent steps which will lead to the need to start the sample movie again.
- New multi-player judgment, false is multi-player, true is single.
- I have added a new high and low frequency node, but I found that you can adjust it by yourselves, I'd rather keep the default, although there are not so many details, but the generality is better, you can adjust the CFG value and noise reduction intensity if you want more details and high and low frequency.

Version v1.0.2
- Bug fix, the image passing is not in order, but all in parallel.

Version v1.0.1
- Changed the face parameter, made the face less like a fake face.

nodes.title: 先读我
widgets_values:
非常重要，必读。

- 推荐的高清修复节点，如果您希望图像更加逼真，甚至包括毛孔细节，请使用此缩放节点。https://openart.ai/workflows/seven947/1minute-8k-upscale/1IPTks1gL7v0EPmvsMcx

我的这个节点使用 Yoloworld 来识别物体，不仅仅只重绘面部和头发，你可以随意组合。

1. 多人 / many prople 节点开启是否多人，多人的话分割蒙版，每个人物单独重绘，否则一起重绘。

2. 如果识别头发的时候识别到了整个头部，请调整 Yoloworld ESAM 里面第一项的参数。

3. 我使用了RemapImageRange来传递图片，如果你不希望传递你可以禁用节点。

高低频使用方法：实测高CFG和高降噪幅度可以大幅度增加画面细节，但是人物面部会变黑，低频同理，如果你会PS的话，使用蒙版刮擦可以获得很好的画面效果。
